{"declarations":[{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.evalSuggestions\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">evalSuggestions</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Tactic/Basic.html#Lean.Elab.Tactic.Tactic\">Elab.Tactic.Tactic</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.evalSuggestions","kind":"def","line":451,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.evalSuggestions","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L451-L464"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.elabSetLibrarySuggestions\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">elabSetLibrarySuggestions</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Elab/Command.html#Lean.Elab.Command.CommandElab\">Elab.Command.CommandElab</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Specify a library suggestion engine.\nNote that Lean does not ship a default library suggestion engine,\nso this is only useful in conjunction with a downstream package which provides one.\n","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.elabSetLibrarySuggestions","kind":"def","line":439,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.elabSetLibrarySuggestions","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L439-L448"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.select\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">select</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">m</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config\">Config</a> := <a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config.mk\">{</a> <a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config.mk\">}</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Suggestion\">Suggestion</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Generate library suggestions for the given metavariable, using the currently registered library suggestions engine. ","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.select","kind":"def","line":420,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.select","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L420-L426"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.getSelector\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">getSelector</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector\">Selector</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.getSelector","kind":"opaque","line":417,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.getSelector","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L417-L418"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">unsafe def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.getSelectorImpl\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">getSelectorImpl</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector\">Selector</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Get the currently registered library suggestions selector by looking up the stored declaration name.\nReturns `none` if no selector is registered or if evaluation fails.\n","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.getSelectorImpl","kind":"def","line":406,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.getSelectorImpl","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L406-L415"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.librarySuggestionsAttr\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">librarySuggestionsAttr</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/Attributes.html#Lean.TagAttribute\">TagAttribute</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Attribute for registering library suggestions selectors. ","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.librarySuggestionsAttr","kind":"opaque","line":398,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.librarySuggestionsAttr","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L398-L404"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.librarySuggestionsExt\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">librarySuggestionsExt</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/EnvExtension.html#Lean.SimplePersistentEnvExtension\">SimplePersistentEnvExtension</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.librarySuggestionsExt","kind":"opaque","line":389,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.librarySuggestionsExt","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L389-L396"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.currentFile\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">currentFile</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector\">Selector</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A library suggestion engine that returns locally defined theorems (those in the current file). ","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.currentFile","kind":"def","line":373,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.currentFile","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L373-L387"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.random\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">random</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">gen</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Data/Random.html#StdGen\">StdGen</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Data/Random.html#StdGen.mk\">{</a> <span class=\"fn\">s1</span> := <span class=\"fn\">37</span>, <span class=\"fn\">s2</span> := <span class=\"fn\">59</span> <a href=\"./Init/Data/Random.html#StdGen.mk\">}</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector\">Selector</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A random premise selection algorithm, provided solely for testing purposes. ","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.random","kind":"def","line":359,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.random","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L359-L371"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.empty\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">empty</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector\">Selector</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The trivial premise selector, which returns no suggestions.\n","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.empty","kind":"def","line":354,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.empty","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L354-L357"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.isDeniedPremise\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">isDeniedPremise</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">env</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Environment.html#Lean.Environment\">Environment</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">name</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">allowPrivate</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a> := <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool.false\">false</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.isDeniedPremise","kind":"def","line":336,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.isDeniedPremise","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L336-L350"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.isDeniedModule\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">isDeniedModule</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">env</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Environment.html#Lean.Environment\">Environment</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">moduleName</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.isDeniedModule","kind":"def","line":333,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.isDeniedModule","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L333-L334"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.typePrefixDenyListExt\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">typePrefixDenyListExt</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/EnvExtension.html#Lean.SimplePersistentEnvExtension\">SimplePersistentEnvExtension</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A premise whose `type.getForallBody.getAppFn` is a constant that has one of these prefixes is not retrieved.\n\nUse `run_cmd modifyEnv fun env => typePrefixDenyListExt.addEntry env typePrefix` to add a type prefix to the deny list.\n","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.typePrefixDenyListExt","kind":"opaque","line":322,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.typePrefixDenyListExt","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L322-L331"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.nameDenyListExt\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">nameDenyListExt</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/EnvExtension.html#Lean.SimplePersistentEnvExtension\">SimplePersistentEnvExtension</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A premise whose name has one of the following components is not retrieved.\n\nUse `run_cmd modifyEnv fun env => nameDenyListExt.addEntry env name` to add a name to the deny list.\n","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.nameDenyListExt","kind":"opaque","line":311,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.nameDenyListExt","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L311-L320"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">opaque</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.moduleDenyListExt\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">moduleDenyListExt</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/EnvExtension.html#Lean.SimplePersistentEnvExtension\">SimplePersistentEnvExtension</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#List\">List</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Premises from a module whose name has one of the following components are not retrieved.\n\nUse `run_cmd modifyEnv fun env => moduleDenyListExt.addEntry env module` to add a module to the deny list.\n","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.moduleDenyListExt","kind":"opaque","line":300,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.moduleDenyListExt","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L300-L309"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector.intersperse\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">Selector</span>.<span class=\"name\">intersperse</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">selector₁ </span><span class=\"fn\">selector₂</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector\">Selector</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">ratio</span> : <a href=\"./Init/Data/Float.html#Float\">Float</a> := <span class=\"fn\">0.5</span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector\">Selector</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Combine two premise selectors by interspersing their results (ignoring scores).\nThe parameter `ratio` (defaulting to 0.5) controls the fraction of suggestions drawn from\n`selector₁` while results are available from both. It is clamped to `[0, 1]`, and ties are\nresolved in favour of `selector₁`.\n\nBoth selectors are asked for the full `maxSuggestions`, rather than a `ratio`-split share, so that\nif one selector returns fewer than its share the other can compensate. This doubles the retrieval\nwork compared to splitting the budget.\n","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector.intersperse","kind":"def","line":244,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector.intersperse","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L244-L294"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector.filterGrindAnnotated\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">Selector</span>.<span class=\"name\">filterGrindAnnotated</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">selector</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector\">Selector</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector\">Selector</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Filter out theorems from grind-annotated modules when the caller is \"grind\".\nModules marked with `grind_annotated` contain manually reviewed/annotated theorems,\nso they should be excluded from automatic premise selection for grind.\nOther callers (like \"simp\") still receive suggestions from these modules.\n","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector.filterGrindAnnotated","kind":"def","line":225,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector.filterGrindAnnotated","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L225-L242"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector.combine\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">Selector</span>.<span class=\"name\">combine</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">selector₁ </span><span class=\"fn\">selector₂</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector\">Selector</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector\">Selector</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Combine two premise selectors, returning the best suggestions. ","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector.combine","kind":"def","line":207,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector.combine","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L207-L223"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector.maxSuggestions\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">Selector</span>.<span class=\"name\">maxSuggestions</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">selector</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector\">Selector</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector\">Selector</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Wrapper for `Selector` that ensures\nthe `maxSuggestions` field in `Config` is respected, post-hoc.\n","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector.maxSuggestions","kind":"def","line":199,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector.maxSuggestions","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L199-L205"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector.postFilter\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">Selector</span>.<span class=\"name\">postFilter</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">selector</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector\">Selector</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector\">Selector</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Respect the `Config.filter` option by implementing it as a post-filter.\nIf a premise selection implementation does not natively handle the filter,\nit should be wrapped with this function.\n","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector.postFilter","kind":"def","line":190,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector.postFilter","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L190-L197"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">def</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.ppSelector\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">ppSelector</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">selector</span> : <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config\">Config</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Suggestion\">Suggestion</a>)</span></span></span></span>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">g</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/Expr.html#Lean.MVarId\">MVarId</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">c</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config\">Config</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <span class=\"fn\">(<a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Array\">Array</a> <a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Suggestion\">Suggestion</a>)</span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"Construct a `Selector` (which acts on an `MVarId`)\nfrom a function which takes the pretty printed goal.\n","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.ppSelector","kind":"def","line":180,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.ppSelector","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L180-L186"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">Selector</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector","kind":"def","line":178,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Selector","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L178-L178"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config.hint\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">Config</span>.<span class=\"name\">hint</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config\">Config</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"An optional arbitrary \"hint\" to the premise selection algorithm.\nThere is no guarantee that the algorithm will make any use of the hint.\n\nPotential use cases include a natural language comment provided by the user\n(e.g. allowing use of the premise selector as a search engine)\nor including context from the current proof and/or file.\n\nWe may later split these use cases into separate fields if necessary.\n","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config.hint","kind":"def","line":176,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config.hint","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L176-L176"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config.filter\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">Config</span>.<span class=\"name\">filter</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config\">Config</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Lean.Name\">Name</a> → <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Lean/Meta/Basic.html#Lean.Meta.MetaM\">MetaM</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Bool\">Bool</a></span></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"A filter on suggestions; only suggestions returning `true` should be returned.\n(It can be better to filter on the premise selection side, to ensure that enough suggestions are returned.)\n","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config.filter","kind":"def","line":165,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config.filter","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L165-L165"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config.caller\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">Config</span>.<span class=\"name\">caller</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config\">Config</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Option\">Option</a> <a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#String\">String</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The tactic that is calling the premise selection, e.g. `simp`, `grind`, or `aesop`.\nThis may be used to adjust the score of the suggestions\n","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config.caller","kind":"def","line":160,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config.caller","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L160-L160"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">abbrev</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config.maxSuggestions\"><span class=\"name\">Lean</span>.<span class=\"name\">LibrarySuggestions</span>.<span class=\"name\">Config</span>.<span class=\"name\">maxSuggestions</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_args\">\n<span class=\"fn\">(<span class=\"fn\">self</span> : <a href=\"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config\">Config</a>)</span></span>\n<span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./Init/Prelude.html#Nat\">Nat</a></div></div>","info":{"doc":"The maximum number of suggestions to return.\n","docLink":"./Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.html#Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config.maxSuggestions","kind":"def","line":155,"name":"Lean.LibrarySuggestions.Config.maxSuggestions","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover/lean4/blob/b4812ae53eea93439ad5dce5a5c26591c31cb697/src/Lean/LibrarySuggestions/Basic.lean#L155-L155"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">constructor</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Lean/